COLL (CASE) A&H Breadth of Inquiry credit'], NULL),
    ('JSTU-J 251', 'INTRODUCTION TO JEWISH HISTORY: FROM THE BIBLE TO SPANISH EXPULSION', '4764', 'Class Status', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 11:10 AM–12:25 PM', 'GA 1122', 'Jeremiah Lockwood', 1, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'GLOBAL & INTERNATIONAL STUDIES', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Topics include the origins of Judaism, Jewish life in ancient Israel and the Diaspora, Judaism and the origins of Christianity, Jewish society and culture under Christian and Muslim rule in the Middle Ages.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd S&H credit
IUB GenEd World Culture credit
